              <p>
                <strong>Next.js + TypeScript:</strong> Server-side rendering, API
                routes, and optimized performance. TypeScript ensures type safety
                across the entire application. <strong>React</strong> handles component
                state and UI interactions, while <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> provides
                utility-first styling. <strong>Flowbite</strong> and <strong
                  >Flowbite-React</strong
                > offer pre-built components that accelerate development.
              </p>
            </div>
