                  d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="my-auto">
              <h4 class="!mb-1 text-xl font-medium text-white">
                Backend & Database
              </h4>
              <p>
                <strong>MongoDB + Mongoose:</strong> NoSQL database for flexible
                team storage and user data management. Mongoose provides schema validation
                and easy querying. <strong>GraphQL</strong> serves as the API layer
                with <strong>Apollo Client</strong> managing queries, mutations,
                and caching on the frontend.
              </p>
